Text: Re Wind Model Cc Here is your spreadsheet There are comments at the bottom each sheet Many of them bring up the same points and I stopped making specific comments at the older projects Sky River and VG comments are more detailed because we are the project partner again as of last week these were divested for QF reasons in On the EnronSumm sheet added are some recommended further info to request and a summary of the main points in the comments On the EnronVal sheet I suggest an alternative valuation for your consideration although issues on which Ive made comments will still need resolution Let me know what I can do for you further and whenif youd like to go over this Cheers Eddie
